{% extends "layouts/page.jinja" %}
{% block title %}Camp Activities{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12 mb-2">
    <h2>Camp Activities</h2>
    <p>
      These are all the different activities for each section to have a go at during <span class="wow">Way Out West!</span> The suggested times for them are on the <a href="{{ url_for('root.programme') }}">the programme</a>, but feel free to do them whenever, and in whatever order works best for you.
    </p>
    <p>
      The WOW! Welcome Pack has lots of useful information, including your section's kit list - download it and have a read. If you haven't already, make sure you <a href="{{ url_for('root.register') }}">sign up for the camp</a> to receive a camp badge and login links for your section's zoom calls.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{ url_for('static', filename='activities/welcome-pack.pdf')}}" class="btn btn-success" target="_blank">Download the WOW! Welcome Pack</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      Don't forget to <a href="{{ url_for('share.new') }}">share your pictures and videos</a> with us so everyone can see what you've been getting up to!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12 mb-3">
    <hr />
  </div>

  {% include "activities/links/combined.jinja" %}

  <div class="col-12 mb-3">
    <hr />
  </div>

  <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
    <h3 id="den-building">Den Building</h3>
    <p>
      Make your den to sleep in for the night, inside or out. Try it out. Set up your sleeping bag, pillow, sleeping mat and donâ€™t forget your cuddly toy. Who's is the most comfortable - take a snap!
    </p>
    <p>
      If you're short of ideas for your den, here are some plans from IKEA!
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="https://www.dezeen.com/2020/05/15/ikea-forts-children-lockdown-coronavirus/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-success">Den Building Blueprints</a>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
    <h3 id="family-quiz">Family Quiz</h3>
    <p>
      Join the whole camp for a fun family quiz on Saturday evening! Grab a pen and paper and join us on the livestream from 7pm.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a class="btn btn-danger" href="{{ url_for('root.live') }}" title="Watch the event livestream">
        <i class="fas fa-video pr-2"></i>Watch live
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
    <h3 id="penny-hike">Penny Hike</h3>
    <p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Make sure you are wearing your group necker.
        </li>
        <li>
          Wear clothes suitable for the weather and shoes that are comfy to walk in.
        </li>
        <li>
          Walk with at least one other adult from your house.
        </li>
        <li>
          Take a coin with you.
        </li>
        <li>
          Whenever you reach a road/path junction, toss your coin - if it's heads turn left, if it's tails turn right.
        </li>
        <li>
          Say hello to any other scouts you see on your hike.
        </li>
        <li>
          Remember to be back home in time for the closing ceremony at 4pm!
        </li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </div>

</div>
{% endblock %}
